title: Cowboy Junkies 2002-10-12 @ Des Moines Civic Center - Des Moines
description:
The venue was very nice, an expansive little theater, and seemed promising for a quiet show, which in fact is what happened. The audience was beautifully appreciative, and the band turned in an absolutely stunning performance, filled with some rarely-played gems. From the first notes of the show opener, Powderfinger, it was apparent that this would be a special night. The highlight for me was Witches, making the drive out and the previous night&#039;s geese-fest all worth it. There isn&#039;t a wasted moment in this entire show, and right after it ended I knew it would always be a favorite.

 

This is the first show from the lower-key 2002 tour in the SOTM download series. I hope you like it as much as I enjoyed it!
